1. *Nasilje* je postalo učestalo u našoj zemlji. (Violence has become frequent in our country.)
2. Nasilje nad ženama je ozbiljan problem. (*Nasilje* is the serious problem against women.)
3. On je bio svjedok *nasilja* na ulici sinoć. (He witnessed *violence* on the street last night.)
4. Uspostavljena je nova organizacija za borbu protiv *nasilja*. (A new organization to fight against *violence* has been established.)
5. Žrtva *nasilja* mora da potraži pomoć. (The victim of *violence* must seek help.)
6. *Nasilnik* je uhapšen od strane policije. (The *violent person* was arrested by the police.)
7. Njegovo ponašanje je dovelo do *nasilja*. (His behavior led to *violence*.)
8. *Nasilničko* ponašanje neće biti tolerisano u ovoj školi. (*Violent* behavior will not be tolerated in this school.)
9. On je optužen za izvršenje *nasilničkog* čina. (He was charged with committing a *violent* act.)
10. Žrtva *nasilja* odlučila je da podigne tužbu protiv napadača. (The victim of *violence* decided to file a lawsuit against the attacker.)